   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ENHANCE ACCESS TO CLEAN WATER &amp; SANITATION</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Water and sanitation are essential for life and health, but they are also essential for a dignified life, empowerment and prosperity. Water and sanitation are human rights, fundamental to every human life. In Kenya, poor sanitation and hygiene as well as unequal access to safe drinking water, in the informal settlements, slums and the rural villages, make thousands of children very sick and at risk of death. Many households spend thousands of shillings in and out of hospital every other day.</narrative>
  </description>
